| Graph Type               | Edge Weight         | Cycles? | Algorithm                         |
| ------------------------ | ------------------- | ------- | --------------------------------- |
| Unweighted               | All 1               | Yes/No  | **BFS**                           |
| Directed Acyclic Graph   | Any (even negative) | No      | **Topological Sort + Relaxation** |
| Weighted Graph           | Positive            | Yes/No  | **Dijkstra**                      |
| Weighted Graph           | Negative edges      | Yes     | **Bellman-Ford**                  |
| All-pairs shortest paths | Any                 | Any     | **Floyd-Warshall**                |
